### MÃ´-Ä‘un vÄƒn hoÃ¡ & cáº£m xÃºc

* *Emotion:* mÃ´ hÃ¬nh phÃ¢n lá»›p (BiGRU/Transformer) trÃªn embedding PhoBERT + Ä‘áº·c trÆ°ng Ã¢m há»c (náº¿u cÃ³). Loss: CE + focal.
